---
import BaseLayout from '@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="Learn about Quakr — built by holders, for holders.">
  <div class="page-content">
    <h1>About Quakr</h1>

    <p>
      <strong>Built by holders, for holders.</strong>
    </p>

    <p>
      Quakr exists because we got tired of hype-driven crypto content that
      never actually shows you how to earn. We're a small team of long-term
      crypto holders who've been staking, lending, and farming since 2019.
      Every guide we publish comes from real experience with real capital.
    </p>

    <h2>What We Cover</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Staking</strong> — PoS delegation, liquid staking, validator selection</li>
      <li><strong>DeFi Yield</strong> — liquidity pools, yield aggregators, risk assessment</li>
      <li><strong>Exchange Lending</strong> — margin funding, savings products, earn programs</li>
      <li><strong>Tools &amp; Security</strong> — hardware wallets, tax software, portfolio tracking</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Our Principles</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We only write about strategies we've used ourselves.</li>
      <li>We always disclose affiliate relationships.</li>
      <li>We never give financial advice — just education.</li>
      <li>We prioritize security and risk awareness in every guide.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Some links on this site are affiliate links. If you sign up through them,
      we earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the
      site running and producing free content. We never let affiliate
      relationships influence our recommendations.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Got a question, suggestion, or correction? Reach out at
      <a href="mailto:hello@quakr.dev">hello@quakr.dev</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
